Functional requirements
    System must find top headlines from the news and their locations
    System must extract Twitter trends from certain locations
    System must match locations of headlines with the Twitter trends
    System must analyze the correlations between news and trends
    System must vizualize the most important endpoints of the research in map and plots


Non-functional requirements
    The system should be able to work on any Web browser
    The system should be available for use 24 hours per day,
    365 days per year
    Any interaction between the user and the system should
    not exceed 5 seconds
    System will use information only from public accouunts
    No authorization is needed to see the results 
